Collateralized Obligation
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The bank has expertise, facilities and access to customers.
 It wants to sell off assets, to free up capital.
 The individual assets are illiquid and risky.
 By pooling them, it allows diversification of risk and improved predicatbility
 of cash flow.
